&lt;h3 id="social-media">Social-Media&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="svg-icons">SVG icons&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://subversive-eu.github.io/hugo-subversive/posts/utilisation/" >List of svg icons&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="share-buttons-">Share Buttons :&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>List of :&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>facebook&lt;/li>
&lt;li>linkedin&lt;/li>
&lt;li>reddit&lt;/li>
&lt;li>telegram&lt;/li>
&lt;li>twitter&lt;/li>
&lt;li>whatsapp&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Be carefull, the navbarShare is not in hidemeta for all posts or page who use /_default/single.html&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>You can add it if you want.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>If you don&amp;rsquo;t want to see the sharebar in list, like homepage, yoursite.com/posts/, yoursite.com/tags(categories / series)/nameoftags/.&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Delete navbarshare in /_default/list.html&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
