&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Installation tricks</title><link>https://subversive-eu.github.io/hugo-subversive/posts/installation/</link><pubDate>Tue, 06 Oct 2020 17:44:04 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://subversive-eu.github.io/hugo-subversive/posts/installation/</guid><description>&lt;p>Hey, I will give you some tricks to make your website.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="favicons">Favicons&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>I used this &lt;a href="https://favicon.io/favicon-generator/">https://favicon.io/favicon-generator/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="deploy">Deploy&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>First, download files listed below :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Paste the files in themes/your-theme/static/&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html"> android-chrome-192x192.png
android-chrome-512x512.png
apple-touch-icon.png
favicon-16x16.png
favicon-32x32.png
favicon.ico
site.webmanifest&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;p>That&amp;rsquo;s all !&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="i18-language">i18 Language&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>To use it, just add and use in &lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/subversive-eu/hugo-subversive/blob/exampleSite/config.yml" >config.yml&lt;/a> :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>languageCode: fr&lt;br>
DefaultContentLanguage: fr&lt;/p>
&lt;p>There is three languages : French(fr), English(en), Spanish(es).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I don&amp;rsquo;t know if there is default language. Be carefull.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Check in themes/your-theme/i18n/ - &lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/subversive-eu/hugo-subversive/tree/main/i18n" >here&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="home-page">Home Page&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>If you want to introduce your website :&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Do not touch in params :&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-yml" data-lang="yml"> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">homeInfoParams&lt;/span>:
&lt;span style="color:#f92672">Title&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">Hi there wave &lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#f92672">Content&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">Can be Info, links, about... &lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>If you just want a list of post + Title, delete it in config.yml&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="markdown">Markdown&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="youtube">Youtube&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>There is a shortcode for youtube video without cookie, and privacy (Only European).&lt;/p>
